<package>
  <description brief="Hardware interface for mobile plattform Slider and robot arm Mover4 by Commonplace Robotics.">

     This node reads the keyboard and generates Twist and/or JointState messeges in a 
     10 Hz loop. For the slider the keys are ws for forward/backward, ad for turn left/right
     and qe for lateral motion which is possible due to the mecanum drive. 

     This node can be tested together with the teleop node in package cpr_robots_teleop. 
     There you can also find a .launch file. 

  </description>
  <author>christian.meyer@cpr-robots.com</author>
  <license>BSD</license>
  <review status="unreviewed" notes=""/>
  <url>http://ros.org/wiki/cpr_robots_hwinterface</url>
  <depend package="roslib"/>
  <depend package="roscpp"/>
  <depend package="std_msgs"/>

</package>


